## Limitations

This report is based on literature available up to October 2023 and may not capture the most recent developments in the field of smart, connected products. Additionally, the analysis is primarily derived from the perspectives of Porter and Heppelmann, which may not encompass all viewpoints or emerging trends in the industry. Further research could explore a broader range of sources and include empirical data to validate the theoretical insights presented.

